snippet: Federal officials say a U.S. jet airliner nearly collided in March with an airborne drone in the sky over Tallahassee, Florida....

headline.print_headline: FAA: Jet Nearly Collided With Drone Over Florida
headline.main: FAA: Jet Nearly Collided With Drone Over Florida

lead_paragraph: Federal officials say a U.S. jet airliner nearly collided in March with an airborne drone in the sky over Tallahassee, Florida.
